<br>
Monday night I was hunting with a group outside Split Paw. It consisted of Myself, a Cleric Soulsculptor, and a Necro Racyn. We have been doing pretty well outside paw but the spawns werent coming fast enough. <br>
<br>
During one of my trips out Quillmane pops up on track. Having never seen this creature before I set off in search. I hadnt traveled too far from camp spot and there he is and NO One is attacking him. I do a quick con (yellow) and ask the group if they can handle. The reply comes back yes so I pull. Me and the necro are dealing most of the damage. I get one heal from the cleric and quill is dead.<br>
<br>
We have been doing split&lt;on&gt;loot, because most of what drops from gnolls is crap. Our friendly neighborhood cleric immediately proceeds to loot quillmane. No problem yet, but it is taking him a long time to loot a corpse. Racyn ask him is he gonna get up? He replies he is checking to see if any mages from his guild are close by to give them cloak. WTF There are mages in our guild who would like to have the cloak. Racyn basically said the same. He says he camped Quill for 3 days without getting the cloak and that it was his. We tell him we need to roll on it. We sent him several tells telling him to roll, no response. Finally he loots the cloak and disbands and logs out. <br>
<br>
About a half hour later a shout goes up in zone from Soulsculptor asking for a ranger to help him track Quillmane. This is BS! I do a shout &quot;dont do it&quot; I could have done worse and explained to the whole zone that he is a loot hawg, but didnt see any sense in it at the time.<br>
<br>
Last night while grouping outside paw again I am in another group and guess who shows up. Soulsculptor. He wants to join our group. I am doing the roll of primary healer for the group and we need a healer bad, but I still told the group leader not to do it. I related the story to the group leader after she asked me &quot;what did he do this time&quot;? As if this guy has a reputaion that is less than desirable.<br>
<br>
It just burns me that this jerk, after that stunt, would even try to get into a group with anyone that he screwed over the night before. <br>
<br>
Ilrissa Silverhand<br>
